topic.title: Now Available: Sixteen Newly Digitized Foreign Relations Volumes
topic.body: This release is part of the Office’s ongoing project, in partnership with the University of Wisconsin Digital Collections Center, to digitize the entire Foreign Relations series. These volumes cover events that took place between 1912 and 1918 and were originally published in print between 1919 and 1933.
